A '''wk'ou melon''' was a double-bulbous, pale red [[Melon/Legends|melon]] from [[Morishim]]. [[Wedge Antilles/Legends|Wedge Antilles]] was harassed by a [[Morish]] [[Gender/Legends|female]] attempting to sell him a melon of this sort while he was on [[Morishim]]. [[Lando Calrissian/Legends|Lando Calrissian]] also purchased one.

